Test#1 Interview REST API task:
There is the following REST API:
1. GET /authors/{author_id} - returns an author
2. POST /authors/{author_id} - adds/updates an author
3. DELETE /authors/{author_id} - removes an author
4. GET /authors/{author_id}/books/{book_id} - returns a book
5. POST /authors/{author_id}/books/{book_id} - adds//updates a book
6. DELETE /authors/{author_id}/books/{book_id} - removes a book

Please write a test case which will cover the following requirement: 
"REQ-2010 The system should allow to add a new book of a particular author"
